What Most “Stock Predictors” Actually Do

Retail thinking:

predict price

Advanced systems actually perform:

detect state transition probability

They are identifying regime changes, not exact prices.

Examples of regimes:
	•	trend
	•	consolidation
	•	volatility expansion
	•	liquidity shock

